org.afplib.afplib

Interface DataObjectFontDescriptor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataObjectFontDescriptorImpl

    public interface DataObjectFontDescriptor
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'Data Object Font Descriptor'.

    The following features are supported:

    • DO Ft Flgs
    • Font Tech
    • VFS
    • HFS
    • Char Rot
    • Enc Env
    • Enc ID
    • Reserved

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getDataObjectFontDescriptor()
